---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Adult Pottery Painting Night"
  description="Adults-only pottery painting for a fun evening out in Centerville, TN. Create beautiful pieces together while bonding."
  price="$20-30 per person"
  duration="1.5-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="adult pottery painting, adults night out, pottery night, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Adult Pottery Painting Night - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Looking for a fun adults-only evening activity? Join us for pottery painting designed exclusively for grown-ups. No kids, no stress—just creativity, laughter, and a relaxing atmosphere perfect for socializing and unwinding.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>This is pottery painting without the kiddie atmosphere. You'll select from a variety of pre-made pieces and paint them in a fun, relaxed setting perfect for adults. Whether you come with friends or solo, you'll enjoy a creative evening that's all about having fun and taking home something beautiful.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Wide selection of pottery pieces to choose from</li>
      <li>All painting supplies, brushes, and paints</li>
      <li>Expert guidance and painting tips</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Adults-only atmosphere</li>
      <li>Take-home your finished piece</li>
      <li>Option: Café refreshments available</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Adults looking for a creative night out</li>
      <li>Friend groups seeking fun activities</li>
      <li>Solo adults wanting to try something new</li>
      <li>Anyone needing a relaxing creative outlet</li>
      <li>Groups celebrating birthdays or special occasions</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome to our adults-only session (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Browse and select your pottery piece (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Paint with guidance and inspiration (60-75 minutes)</li>
      <li>Add finishing touches (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Take home your masterpiece</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $20-30 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1.5-2 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> No experience needed—all levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your adults-only pottery night!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Finally, a pottery painting experience just for adults! The atmosphere was so fun and relaxed. Great night out with friends!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Sarah</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"I brought three friends for a birthday celebration. We laughed, created, and loved every minute. No kids around was perfect!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Amanda</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Such a fun way to unwind after a long week. The staff was great and the adults-only vibe made it extra enjoyable!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Jessica</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Ladies Night Pottery Painting</h3>
        <p>Girls' night out pottery painting and creative bonding.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-classes/ladies-night-pottery-painting" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Date Night Pottery Painting</h3>
        <p>Romantic pottery painting experience for couples.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-classes/date-night-pottery-painting" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Team Building Pottery Painting</h3>
        <p>Corporate team building through creative pottery painting.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-classes/team-building-pottery-painting" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
